// Attack: if development mode is active, AliasResourceMetaImpl is created with
// realResourceName = JSF_UNCOMPRESSED_JS_RESOURCE_NAME (hardcoded constant)
// The libraryExists probe:
// GET /myapp/javax.faces.resource/jsf.js?ln=WEB-INF HTTP/1.1
